.Dd February 20, 2026
.Dt FLUXSNAP 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm fluxsnap
.Nd hotkey tiler with zone-based layout for Fluxbox/X11
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl c Ar config
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
retiles windows using configured zones and spacing.
It honors
.Pa _NET_WORKAREA
so Fluxbox toolbar/slit space is respected.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Fl c Ar config
Path to a configuration file.
.It Fl h
Show usage help.
.El
.Sh CONFIGURATION
Supported keys:
.Bl -tag -width zone
.It Ic modifier
Super, Mod4, Alt, Mod1, Ctrl, Control, or Shift.
.It Ic hotkey
X keysym string (for example: space, F12, Return).
.It Ic gap
Global outer gap from monitor/workarea edges.
.It Ic zone
Repeatable zone definition:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
zone=name,x_pct,y_pct,w_pct,h_pct,layout,max_windows,zone_gap
.Ed
.Pp
Zone layout modes:
.Bl -bullet -compact
.It
rows
.It
cols
.It
grid
.El
.Pp
When
.Ic max_windows
is 0, the zone accepts unlimited windows.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr fluxbox 1
